&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking an experienced and committed Administrator with excellent communication skills to join our Organisation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post holder will provide a wide range of administrative support services for the Senior Management Team and Board.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;They will be expected to work without immediate supervision, to enable the corporate team to carry out a range of activity as quickly and effectively as required. Nexus Health Group is a forward thinking organisation with a long history of providing good quality primary care in Southwark, working across 9 sites based in North Southwark.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Refer to Job Description for details on the post, including main duties and responsibilities.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Closing Date:  6th November 2020&lt;/p&gt;
